    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this absolute gem. It is in truly stunning shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it shows in every little detail. No dings, no scratches, just a smooth, flawless ride that's ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for that 'brand new' feel without the brand new price tag, you've found it! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
