      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional example of a meticulously maintained vehicle, presented in showroom condition. This car has been strictly garage-kept and remains entirely free of any exterior blemishes, stone chips, or door dings. The factory paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather seating shows zero wear, the carpets have been protected by original floor mats since day one, and it has never been smoked in. Mechanically, it is flawless, having followed a rigorous manufacturer-recommended service schedule with all records available for review. With incredibly low mileage and a recent comprehensive inspection, this vehicle drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. It is a turn-key opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast seeking a pristine driving experience.",
